name='Carl Data/antenna totally unfolded.csv'
df=pd.read_csv(name,sep=',')
df

f=np.array(df['Frequency(Hz)'])
Rs=df['Rs']
Zs=df['Xs']

fig, ax=plt.subplots()

ax.plot(f,Rs, color='b', label='Real Part')
ax2=ax.twinx()
ax2.plot(f,Zs,color='r',label='Imaginary Part')

plt.title('Impedance vs. Frequency for Unfolded Antenna')
ax.set_xlabel('Frequency (Hz)')
ax.set_ylabel('Re(Impedance) (ohms)')
ax2.set_ylabel('Im(Impedance) (ohms)')

ax2.legend(loc='upper left')
ax.legend(loc='upper center', bbox_to_anchor=(1.5, 0.8), shadow=True, ncol=1)
ax2.legend(loc='upper center', bbox_to_anchor=(1.5, .7), shadow=True, ncol=1)
